Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.21,0:22:01.92,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}認めていた臆病な過去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.96,0:22:07.88,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}わからないままに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.88,0:22:12.97,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}怖がっていた　後ろの自分が現実を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.97,0:22:18.69,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}今に映す
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.69,0:22:24.03,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}いくつもの空を描いた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.07,0:22:28.70,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}ここはきっと　儚い心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.70,0:22:31.41,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}乱して
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.41,0:22:32.07,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}夢で！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.07,0:22:35.83,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}高く跳んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.83,0:22:42.13,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}躰は　どんな不安纏っても振り払っていく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.13,0:22:46.55,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}眠る　小さな想い
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.55,0:22:50.72,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}拡がり出して　気付く　弱い私
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.72,0:22:54.56,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}君がいれば　暗い世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.56,0:22:57.48,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}強くいれた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.06,0:23:03.15,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}長い夢見る心は　そう　永遠で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.65,0:23:07.32,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}I wanna always stay with you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.36,0:23:12.62,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}I give you every thing I have
Comment: 0,0:21:19.25,0:21:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OPCH
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.21,0:22:01.92,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}面對過去懦弱的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.96,0:22:07.88,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}即使仍是懵懵懂懂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.88,0:22:18.69,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}害怕如今的自己 身後的映出的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.69,0:22:24.03,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}萬物繪出的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.07,0:22:28.70,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}卻是顆脆弱無比的心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.70,0:22:31.41,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}以此為目標
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.41,0:22:32.07,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}在夢想中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.07,0:22:35.83,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}展翅高飛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.83,0:22:42.13,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}不管身體為多少不安鎖住 都將其拂去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.13,0:22:46.55,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}守住那小小的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.55,0:22:50.72,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}察覺到不斷蔓延的 羸弱的我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.72,0:22:57.48,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}若此世有你 黑暗的世界裡我也能堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.06,0:23:03.15,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}在無盡的夢裡 我心永恆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.65,0:23:07.32,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}與君相伴 直至天荒地老
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.36,0:23:12.62,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}我將為你 獻出我的所有
